description: Unbelievable - I managed another threesome! This summer was very generous with boys in need for money. I went for a coffee with my good friend who just returned from Thailand. While we were talking, I spotted two adorable guys sipping coffee a few tables away from us. I left the friend to his coffee and started chatting with the boys. They were just hanging out so we had plenty of time to talk. What they didn´t have, was money. Summer was coming to an end and they wanted to do some hardcore partying. They were totally broke- so no parties for them. This was their lucky day because I wanted to party with them. They agreed but I doubt it was the party they hoped for. I took them to an abandoned car wreckage site and fucked them hard.
title: Czech Hunter 315
